<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Peder Kjølhede was a Danish-Lutheran pastor who served in Muskegon, Grayling, and other Michigan cities.</p>
</bioghist>


<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The Peder Kjølhede papers consists mainly of his sermons and sermon notes, with some photographs and miscellaneous records of various church functions and celebrations.</p>
</scopecontent>

